# InventoScan Design System

## 🎨 Visual Identity

### Farbpalette
```css
/* Dark Theme - Primär */
--background-primary: #0A0E27;     /* Dunkles Blau-Schwarz */
--background-secondary: #151932;   /* Karten-Hintergrund */
--background-elevated: #1E2139;    /* Erhöhte Elemente */

/* Akzentfarben */
--accent-primary: #6366F1;         /* Indigo */
--accent-secondary: #8B5CF6;       /* Purple */
--accent-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1 0%, #8B5CF6 100%);

/* Text */
--text-primary: #FFFFFF;
--text-secondary: #94A3B8;         /* Grau-Blau */
--text-muted: #64748B;

/* Status */
--success: #10B981;
--warning: #F59E0B;
--danger: #EF4444;

/* Borders & Overlays */
--border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
--glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
```

### Typography
```css
/* Font Stack */
--font-primary: 'Inter', -apple-system, system-ui, sans-serif;
--font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;

/* Größen */
--text-xs: 0.75rem;    /* 12px */
--text-sm: 0.875rem;   /* 14px */
--text-base: 1rem;     /* 16px */
--text-lg: 1.125rem;   /* 18px */
--text-xl: 1.25rem;    /* 20px */
--text-2xl: 1.5rem;    /* 24px */
--text-3xl: 1.875rem;  /* 30px */
--text-4xl: 2.25rem;   /* 36px */

/* Font Weights */
--font-normal: 400;
--font-medium: 500;
--font-semibold: 600;
--font-bold: 700;
```

## 🏗 Layout-Struktur

### Dashboard Layout
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Sidebar (240px)  │      Main Content        │
│                   │                          │
│  - Logo           │  ┌────────────────────┐ │
│  - Navigation     │  │   Stats Cards Row   │ │
│  - User Profile   │  └────────────────────┘ │
│                   │                          │
│                   │  ┌────────────────────┐ │
│                   │  │   Product Grid     │ │
│                   │  │  ┌────┐ ┌────┐    │ │
│                   │  │  │Card │ │Card │    │ │
│                   │  │  └────┘ └────┘    │ │
│                   │  └────────────────────┘ │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Component Specifications

#### Stats Card
```tsx
<div className="stats-card">
  <div className="stats-icon">{icon}</div>
  <div className="stats-content">
    <p className="stats-label">Label</p>
    <h3 className="stats-value">1,234</h3>
    <span className="stats-change">+12%</span>
  </div>
</div>
```

```css
.stats-card {
  background: var(--background-secondary);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 24px;
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.stats-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
}
```

#### Product Card
```tsx
<div className="product-card">
  <div className="product-image">
    <img src={image} alt={title} />
    <div className="product-overlay">
      <button className="quick-action">View</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div className="product-info">
    <h3>{title}</h3>
    <p className="product-meta">{category}</p>
    <div className="product-footer">
      <span className="product-price">{price}</span>
      <span className="product-status">{status}</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

## 🎯 UI Components

### Buttons
```css
/* Primary Button */
.btn-primary {
  background: var(--accent-gradient);
  color: white;
  padding: 12px 24px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-weight: 600;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

/* Ghost Button */
.btn-ghost {
  background: transparent;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  padding: 12px 24px;
  border-radius: 8px;
}

/* Icon Button */
.btn-icon {
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--glass);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
}
```

### Upload Area
```tsx
<div className="upload-area">
  <div className="upload-icon">📸</div>
  <h3>Drop images here</h3>
  <p>or click to browse</p>
  <div className="upload-formats">
    JPG, PNG, WEBP up to 10MB
  </div>
</div>
```

```css
.upload-area {
  background: var(--glass);
  border: 2px dashed var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 48px;
  text-align: center;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.upload-area:hover {
  border-color: var(--accent-primary);
  background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05);
}

.upload-area.dragging {
  border-color: var(--accent-secondary);
  background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
}
```

## 📱 Responsive Breakpoints
```css
/* Mobile First */
--mobile: 0px;        /* Default */
--tablet: 768px;      /* md: */
--desktop: 1024px;    /* lg: */
--wide: 1280px;       /* xl: */
--ultrawide: 1536px;  /* 2xl: */
```

## 🎭 Animations

### Transitions
```css
/* Standard Easing */
--ease-in-out: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
--ease-out: cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1);
--ease-in: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 1, 1);

/* Durations */
--duration-fast: 150ms;
--duration-normal: 300ms;
--duration-slow: 500ms;
```

### Hover Effects
```css
/* Card Hover */
.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}

/* Glow Effect */
.glow:hover {
  box-shadow: 
    0 0 20px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3),
    0 0 40px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
}
```

## 🖼 Image Gallery Layout

### Grid View
```css
.image-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 24px;
}

.image-item {
  aspect-ratio: 1;
  border-radius: 12px;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
  background: var(--background-secondary);
}

.image-item img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.image-item:hover img {
  transform: scale(1.1);
}
```

## 📊 Dashboard Widgets

### Chart Container
```css
.chart-container {
  background: var(--background-secondary);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 24px;
  height: 400px;
}

.chart-header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
```

### Table Design
```css
.data-table {
  background: var(--background-secondary);
  border-radius: 12px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.data-table th {
  background: var(--background-elevated);
  padding: 16px;
  text-align: left;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.data-table td {
  padding: 16px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.data-table tr:hover {
  background: var(--glass);
}
```

## 🔧 Tailwind Config (falls verwendet)

```js
// tailwind.config.js
module.exports = {
  theme: {
    extend: {
      colors: {
        'bg-primary': '#0A0E27',
        'bg-secondary': '#151932',
        'bg-elevated': '#1E2139',
        'accent': {
          primary: '#6366F1',
          secondary: '#8B5CF6',
        }
      },
      backdropBlur: {
        xs: '2px',
      },
      backgroundImage: {
        'gradient-primary': 'linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1 0%, #8B5CF6 100%)',
      }
    }
  }
}
```

## 📝 Claude Code Instruktionen

### MUST FOLLOW:
1. **Dark Theme Only** - Kein Light Mode Toggle
2. **Card-Based Layout** - Alle Inhalte in Karten
3. **Glassmorphism** - Subtle backdrop-blur Effekte
4. **Gradient Akzente** - Nur für wichtige CTAs
5. **Hover-Animationen** - Smooth transitions auf allen interaktiven Elementen

### NEVER DO:
- Keine harten Schatten (nur soft shadows)
- Keine pure white (#FFFFFF) Hintergründe
- Keine rechteckigen Buttons (immer border-radius)
- Keine statischen Cards (immer hover effects)
- Kein Comic Sans (obviously)

---

**Dieses Design-System ist verbindlich für alle UI-Entwicklungen in InventoScan.**